-- Invesco's first-quarter profit falls 15.5 percent
-- 
-- Thu May 01, 2014 07:46AM EDT
-- None



NEW YORK, May 1 (Reuters) - Invesco Ltd <IVZ.N>, which oversees the PowerShares line of exchange-traded funds, said on Thursday that its first-quarter profit fell 15.5 percent as business operating expenses increased.

